responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "50EA897B4EFCE4918C64D4BBF7FFCEE5", "Come and dance five sisters of Sephillion. Dance the dance and wish for me. Helea my dearest, what wonders do you wish to see? I dream of glint heavy and free. A personal hoard piled high and only for me.")
